name: Supreme Duelist Stickman Map
summary: Learn about .FUN files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: Supreme Duelist Stickman is a fighting game in which players play as stick people that move using ragdoll physics. Each Supreme Duelist Stickman battle takes place in a fighting arena that is saved as a FUN file.

In Supreme Duelist Stickman's Map Editor, players can create and save their own FUN files. Many map creators share their custom FUN files online, allowing other players to download, import, and use them in Supreme Duelist Stickman.

instructions: You can open a FUN file with Supreme Duelist Stickman (Android, iOS). To do so, open the game's Map Editor and select load map. Then, navigate to and open your FUN file.
